{"tid":1369343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[大家還記得嗎?] 不割蓆、不譴責、不篤灰、不流血、不被捕","createTime":"2019-07-26T16:23:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T08:56:49.000Z","uid":113300,"like":212,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"2237d48d82292e1cc57f84f2b17d378271ea0344","tid":1369343,"uid":113300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:23:15.000Z","msg":"大家仲記唔記得時至今日我地仲keep到繼續呢場運動嘅信念係咩?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不割蓆、不譴責、不篤灰、不流血、不被捕</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山 各自努力</span></span><br />\n以現時形勢要做到不流血、不被捕似乎有d困難<br />\n但係有三樣我地絕對係可以輕鬆並且要堅持做到<br />\n不割蓆、不譴責、不篤灰係呢場運動嘅核心價值我相信無人反對<br />\n<br />\n依家出面有好多分化post<br />\n我唔知係3毛嘅例牌夜晚帶風向還是手足嘅真實諗法<br />\n<br />\n如果係3毛帶風向只證明一樣野<br />\n就係我地對家真係好驚<br />\n3毛帶風向都唔係始於今晚<br />\n次次有遊行前都必然出現<br />\n大家都無俾人拉走 係咪?<br />\n我相信大家仍然可以保持獨立思考<br />\n<br />\n如果係手足諗法<br />\n大家必須係當一個意見咁看待 唔好盲從<br />\n必須要經過自己嘅大腦去諗一諗<br />\n亦都要尊重各位手足嘅想法<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n<br />\n和理非嘅你<br />\n千祈唔好又左膠化<br />\n你今日仲同人講打不還手係無可能嘅事<br />\n尤其是經過元朗一役<br />\n我亦都理解你地嘅意見係唔想手足受傷同埋怕影響民意<br />\n我亦都唔支持入村 但人不犯我我不犯人<br />\n打必還手就係咁簡單 同時亦都係為咗保護同行者<br />\n<br />\n勇武派嘅你<br />\n香港人嘅憤怒係一種共識<br />\n唔好以為淨係得你好嬲<br />\n和理非手足都係給予一種關懷<br />\n同時由6.9到今日 或者再早d由雨傘計<br />\n大大小小嘅衝突我相信已經成為一種寶貴經驗<br />\n足以你地喺前線做出可靠決定<br />\n我絕對相信你地<br />\n<br />\n大家仲記得矛盾論嗎?<br />\n勇武派係和理非嘅矛<br />\n和理非係勇武派嘅盾<br />\n2014年和理非輸咗<br />\n2016年勇武派輸咗<br />\n2019年兩面互相配合香港人先可以有咁大嘅力量<br />\n如果依家先嚟分化你覺得可惜嗎?可笑嗎?<br />\n對唔對得住各位烈士、義士、死士?<br />\n我在此懇請 大家要相信對方<br />\n<br />\n最後我想各位聽一聽LMF嘅揸緊中指<br />\n聽清楚睇清楚首歌嘅內容<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XgKazvhNYz8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXgKazvhNYz8&d=vhywW4AIbf33TEOu71%2FwU%2FsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=74172d4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XgKazvhNYz8</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我並唔認同你講既一切一切<br />\n但我會捍衛 即使死不眼閉<br />\n並唔認為你所謂既需要剋制<br />\n會帶黎公平 穩定壓倒一切</span></strong><br />\n正正就係矛盾論<br />\n<br />\n你不要放棄 堅持到尾<br />\n自由要接捧 我地要靠哂你<br />\n不管犧牲幾多 揸緊中指我道理<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不自由 毋寧死</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n妥協最後 失敗者只會係你<br />\n不能容忍 世界變成咁<br />\n犧牲幾多 揸緊中指我道理<br />\n<br />\n各位切記切記<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆、不譴責、不篤灰</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山 各自努力</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">727元朗見</span></span>"},{"pid":"2edeae3c3d6cc66e9bc40f30f8106c88118d211b","tid":1369343,"uid":113300,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:25:17.000Z","msg":"推一推<br />\n<br />\n歡迎各位討論"},{"pid":"3342947904a4267dd54a08a725c6dc8ae3918577","tid":1369343,"uid":113300,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:27:17.000Z","msg":"學Rock Gor話齋<br />\n鍾意嘅俾個like我 唔鍾意嘅入嚟屌7我"},{"pid":"eca42f972d1e9210c52567f8d108a7b9d2f1f051","tid":1369343,"uid":178933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:28:31.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"4adf33a6c4bdda638750a778a6a7cb90210cd352","tid":1369343,"uid":275723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:30:06.000Z","msg":"push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1222840dd190d7a6c2e14e624018cbd9664de04","tid":1369343,"uid":113300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:30:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"25b90493d304db3135e7ef8c650ba7be03ec6819","tid":1369343,"uid":288670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:31:23.000Z","msg":"一定要推<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"998a69fccdd81f3258381d28b0748df8ed9b89ce","tid":1369343,"uid":275564,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:33:40.000Z","msg":"今次要用和理非，勇武暫時讓路一次先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留力728港島西<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32cf11bad0217ff65f308cacf472a3ef9c8d0511","tid":1369343,"uid":288670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"998a69fccdd81f3258381d28b0748df8ed9b89ce","tid":1369343,"uid":275564,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:33:40.000Z","msg":"今次要用和理非，勇武暫時讓路一次先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留力728港島西<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:34:24.000Z","msg":"收撚皮啦"},{"pid":"8d9912b31a1209ae472f8da3b9830fd2fdecf93a","tid":1369343,"uid":113300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:37:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d824af741322fa41e71e7631bb12e14e1629558b","tid":1369343,"uid":167132,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:37:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0753461e6291d8ea1b0c582f462e19cfa933c82e","tid":1369343,"uid":237517,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:38:03.000Z","msg":"相信現場智慧 不受傷 不被捕 不割席<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n每晚都會有五毛分化 照舊冷待 用力推有用保護手足既post就得"},{"pid":"41dde563f107a39b487b91eb313a066e425cae83","tid":1369343,"uid":276208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:38:26.000Z","msg":"借位一用<br />\n<br />\n<strong>請幫推到鄉民見到，希望聽日可以相安無事</strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">誠懇請鄉民今次真係要<ins>阻止任何可疑人士（包括疑似示威者）入村</ins>，唔係又引起誤會／衝突就唔好啦~~ </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n[投訴懶人包] 反對套丁及冒充原居民 「修補撕裂，由我做起，幫助原居民保家衛族」<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1369127\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1369127</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: blue;\">齊上齊落，支持五大訴求<br />\n支持圍村去黑，還我平靜鄉郊<br />\n反恐反黑，由投訴撚做起</span></em>"},{"pid":"9b6f5a342f73e953fb77ac4f6d3aa2d9bf804704","tid":1369343,"uid":113300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:40:43.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"63260745111f2ada1d8bbb456b5f5e387df03bf4","tid":1369343,"uid":258028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:41:31.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"e73d51d8383764846b76802f6463cdf02c4d11fa","tid":1369343,"uid":113300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:44:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">齊上齊落</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">對準政權</span></span>"},{"pid":"63445c996a4184011420842c6852398239462ff9","tid":1369343,"uid":113300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:47:14.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n大家要保持獨立思考"},{"pid":"3b06a693cfd07167ce3ddf53e4e15964fb29199e","tid":1369343,"uid":113300,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:51:02.000Z","msg":"依家政府切乜都冇用<br />\n<br />\n對準真雙普選<br />\n<br />\n再要求特赦義士"},{"pid":"e20192bf72fdbc6c51edf070689176324657771c","tid":1369343,"uid":46413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:52:32.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"5b47377b2e3969cd0a1e8dbdcf91fc36f3b596f8","tid":1369343,"uid":280830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:53:17.000Z","msg":"be water"},{"pid":"d0fe8e3e8db8d8677388b879279d85c034e40370","tid":1369343,"uid":85395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:56:29.000Z","msg":"不割蓆<br />\n不譴責<br />\n不篤灰<br />\n不流血<br />\n不被捕"},{"pid":"2ad621cd9b23d554d8cb6e383d6a29ce091296b3","tid":1369343,"uid":113300,"like":1,"dislike":